# Project: jaspersmet-astro

Jasper Smet's personal site and blog — a multilingual static site built with Astro.

## Tech Stack

| Layer          | Technology                                                                 |
| -------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Framework      | [Astro v5](https://astro.build) (SSG, `.astro` + `.mdx` pages)            |
| Language       | TypeScript (strict mode), JavaScript for endpoints (`rss.xml.js`, `llms.txt.js`) |
| Runtime        | Node.js 22                                                                |
| Package mgr    | npm                                                                        |
| Styling        | [Tailwind CSS v4](https://tailwindcss.com) + [daisyUI v5](https://daisyui.com) |
| Typography     | `@tailwindcss/typography` plugin for `prose` classes                       |
| Markdown       | MDX (`@astrojs/mdx`) with Shiki syntax highlighting                        |
| Content        | Astro Content Collections (`src/content/config.ts`)                        |
| i18n           | Astro built-in i18n routing + custom `src/i18n/` translation helpers       |
| RSS            | `@astrojs/rss`                                                             |
| Sitemap        | `@astrojs/sitemap`                                                         |
| Comments       | [Giscus](https://giscus.app) (GitHub Discussions)                          |
| Analytics      | Simple Analytics (scripts.simpleanalyticscdn.com)                          |
| Fonts          | Lexend via bunny.net                                                       |
| CI/CD          | GitHub Actions → GitHub Pages                                              |

## Project Structure

```
.
├── .github/workflows/deploy.yml   # CI: build + deploy to GitHub Pages
├── astro.config.mjs               # Astro config (site, i18n, integrations, Vite plugins)
├── tsconfig.json                  # Extends astro/tsconfigs/strict
├── public/                        # Static assets served at /
│   ├── avatar.webp
│   ├── favicon.svg
│   ├── glaze-logo.svg
│   └── sugar-logo.svg
└── src/
    ├── components/                # Reusable Astro components
    │   ├── ContactForm.astro
    │   ├── Footer.astro
    │   ├── GiscusComments.astro   # Giscus script loader
    │   ├── Header.astro
    │   ├── HeroAmbient.astro      # Decorative hero background (orbs + gradients)
    │   ├── HighlightCards.astro
    │   ├── PostTeaser.astro       # Blog post card (image, title, date, excerpt)
    │   ├── ProjectCards.astro
    │   ├── SEO.astro              # <head> meta tags, OG, Twitter cards
    │   └── SocialLinks.astro
    ├── content/
    │   ├── config.ts              # Content collection schema (blog)
    │   └── blog/                  # Blog posts as MDX with images
    │       ├── 2026/...
    │       ├── cakephp-doc-migration/
    │       ├── cakephp-mercure/
    │       └── sqlite-ft5-for-search-api/
    ├── i18n/
    │   ├── index.ts               # t() helper, getSiteData(), getProjects(), etc.
    │   ├── en.ts                  # English translation keys
    │   ├── nl.ts                  # Dutch translation keys
    │   └── fr.ts                  # French translation keys
    ├── layouts/
    │   ├── BaseLayout.astro       # Root layout: <html>, SEO, Header, Footer, drawer nav, theme toggle
    │   └── BlogPostLayout.astro   # Blog post layout: article + Giscus comments
    ├── pages/
    │   ├── index.astro            # English homepage (hero, highlights, projects, recent posts)
    │   ├── contact.astro          # English contact page
    │   ├── rss.xml.js             # RSS feed endpoint (GET)
    │   ├── llms.txt.js            # LLM-friendly site index endpoint
    │   ├── posts/
    │   │   ├── index.astro        # Blog listing page (all posts, sorted by date)
    │   │   └── [...slug].astro    # Dynamic blog post route
    │   ├── fr/                    # French localized pages (index, contact, posts)
    │   └── nl/                    # Dutch localized pages (index, contact, posts)
    ├── styles/
    │   └── global.css             # Tailwind imports + daisyUI themes (spring-fun, spring-night) + custom animations
    └── utils/                     # (currently empty)
```

## i18n System

- **Locales**: `en` (default, no prefix), `nl` (`/nl/`), `fr` (`/fr/`)
- **Routing**: prefixDefaultLocale is `false`, so English URLs have no prefix
- **Translation function**: `t(locale, key, params?)` — dot-notation key lookup, supports `{param}` interpolation
- **Site data**: `getSiteData(locale)` returns nav, hero, and description per locale
- **Page-specific data**: `getPostsPageData()`, `getContactPageData()`, `getHomepageHighlights()`, `getHomepageIntro()` all accept a locale
- Translation key files are plain TypeScript objects (`as const`)

## Content (Blog)

- Defined in `src/content/config.ts` using `defineCollection` with Zod schema
- **Schema fields**: `title` (string), `description` (string), `date` (Date), `tags` (string[], default []), `draft` (boolean, default false), `image` (optional image)
- Posts are `.mdx` files in `src/content/blog/`, each in its own folder with associated images
- Draft posts are filtered out on the homepage and blog listing
- Posts are sorted by `date` descending

## Styling Conventions

- **Tailwind CSS v4** with `@import "tailwindcss"` (not `@tailwind` directives)
- **daisyUI v5** imported as a Tailwind plugin; two custom themes defined inline:
  - `spring-fun` (light, default)
  - `spring-night` (dark)
- Theme toggle via `<input data-theme-toggle>` checkbox and inline script in BaseLayout
- Custom CSS layers in `global.css`: `@layer base` (selection colors), `@layer components` (highlight-card, hero-ambient classes, keyframe animations)
- Default font: Lexend (variable weight 100–900)
- DaisyUI component classes used throughout (btn, card, drawer, divider, menu, avatar, etc.)

## Key Integration Details

- **Giscus comments**: loaded on blog posts via `GiscusComments.astro`; repo `josbeir/personal-blog`, category "Announcements", uses `preferred_color_scheme`
- **Theme persistence**: localStorage key `theme` (values: `light`/`dark`), falls back to `prefers-color-scheme` media query
- **SEO**: `SEO.astro` generates `<title>`, meta description, canonical, OG, and Twitter card tags; falls back to avatar.webp as default OG image
- **RSS**: served at `/rss.xml`, English-only, includes all blog posts
- **llms.txt**: served at `/llms.txt`, lists all pages and blog post URLs for LLM consumption
- **Simple Analytics**: loaded asynchronously in `<head>`, no custom configuration

## Deployment

- **Host**: GitHub Pages (`https://www.jaspersmet.be`)
- **CI**: GitHub Actions workflow at `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`
  - Trigger: push to `main`, or manual `workflow_dispatch`
  - Node 22, `npm ci`, `npm run build`
  - Artifact upload (`actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3`) from `dist/`
  - Deploy via `actions/deploy-pages@v4`

## Scripts

| Command           | Description                |
| ----------------- | -------------------------- |
| `npm run dev`     | Start Astro dev server     |
| `npm run start`   | Alias for `dev`            |
| `npm run build`   | Production build to `dist/`|
| `npm run preview` | Preview production build   |

## Development Notes

- The `dist/` and `.astro/` directories are gitignored
- The `old/` directory is excluded from TypeScript compilation (likely contains legacy/migration artifacts)
- The project is strictly typed (`strictNullChecks: true`, `allowJs: true`)
- No testing framework, linter, or formatter is currently configured
- Blog posts are the only content collection; there is no CMS — content is authored directly in MDX files
- The `ContactForm.astro` component exists but there is no visible backend form handler; forms likely rely on an external service or are static placeholders
